    Closeable, AutoCloseable, ChangedReadersObserver, InternalScanner, KeyValueScanner, Shipper

    @InterfaceAudience.Private
public class MobStoreScanner
extends StoreScanner
    Scanner scans both the memstore and the MOB Store. Coalesce KeyValue stream into List<KeyValue> for a single row.

      • next

        public boolean next(List<Cell> outResult,
                    ScannerContext ctx)
             throws IOException
        Firstly reads the cells from the HBase. If the cell are a reference cell (which has the reference tag), the scanner need seek this cell from the mob file, and use the cell found from the mob file as the result.
        指定者:
        next 在接口中 InternalScanner
        覆盖:
        next 在类中 StoreScanner
        参数:
        outResult - return output array
        返回:
        true if there are more rows, false if scanner is done
        抛出:
        IOException - e
